When adding Subrepos via SourceTree we write the definition .hgsub file:
{code}
subrepo=https://URL//Repo/
{code}

According to [HG docs|http://mercurial.selenic.com/wiki/Subrepository#Use_.27trivial.27_subrepo_paths_where_possible] - we should trivial paths.
We should consider changing this behavior in SourceTree.
